<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7037507>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–5. Edaphus nagugushikuensis sp. n., holotype male. Dorsal habitus, excluding posterior portion of abdomen (1); abdominal sternite VIII (2); sperm pump (photographed through abdominal tergite) (3); aedeagus in dorsal view (4, 5)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7037507/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

